Maintainer: Brice Goglin <Brice.Goglin@ens-lyon.org>
Build-Depends-Indep: debhelper (>= 4.0.2)
Standards-Version: 3.6.1

Package: llgal
Architecture: all
Depends: imagemagick, ${perl:Depends}, libimage-size-perl
Suggests: exiftags
Provides: igal
Replaces: igal, igal-text
Description: Loulous gallery
 llgal is a on-line gallery generator.
 It is based on igal (most of the interface is the same).
 llgal adds supports for different types of slides including movies,
 text, links and subdirectories, addition of headers and footers in
 generated HTML files, and a few other options.
 Caption may be automatically generated from JPEG EXIF tags.
